title: WELCOME
visual_description: Welcome to the generator room. You are going to inspect the generator room now.

title: SAFETY - EAR PROTECTION
visual_description: Please wear ear protection device before you go inside the generator room.

title: SAFETY - HELMET WITH LIGHT
visual_description: Please wear a safety helmet with light before enter the generator room.

title: SAFETY - SWITCH ON LIGHT
visual_description: Please switch on  helmet light.

visual_description: Now you are about to inspect the synchronize panel. Be sure you are currently placed in front of the synchronize panel.

visual_description: Check whether emergency switch of synchronize panel is working.

title: SYNC. PANEL - SYS. CONTROL SWITCH
visual_description: Check system control switch

title: SYNC. PANEL - LOAD DEMAND SWITCH

title: SYNC. PANEL - LOAD DEMAND DROPOUT

visual_description: Check demand pickup

title: SYNC. PANEL - LOAD UNIT SELECTION
visual_description: Check load unit selection

title: SYNC. PANEL - EARTH FAULT RELAY 01
visual_description: Check Earth Fault Relay 1

visual_description: Check Earth Fault Relay 2

title: GENERATOR 01 - OFF MODE

title: GEN. 01 - BATTERY PACK
visual_description: Check generator 01 battery water level and report whether water level is OK or NOT OK.

title: GEN. 01 - ENGINE OIL LEAKS
visual_description: Check generator 01 body for oil leaks and report OK if oil leaks not available and NOT OK if oil leaks available.

title: GEN. 01 - BATTERY VOLTAGE
